		<h1> Scheduling Tool </h1>
		<p class="no_headline"> One of the early features that I concepted and designed was an online scheduling tool. I created a 4 step process in order to get the required information for our agents. One of the challenges of working for Urban Compass was that I always had to think of 3 parties: The User, The Agent, and the Landlord. All three of these people were crucial in the final result of finding an apartment, and it was always a challenge making sure the process was simple for all parties. <p>
